    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "cold-suffering bird",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "冬の澄んだ空気の中、一羽の寒苦鳥が枝でじっと寒さを耐えていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "詩人は、荒涼とした風景の中で寒苦鳥の姿を描写し、その孤独を表現した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "雪景色の中、寒苦鳥が小さく鳴き、冬の厳しさを伝えているようだった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "木枯らしが吹きすさぶ中、寒苦鳥は懸命に生き抜こうとしていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "(lazy) person who is poor at practicing asceticism",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "彼は修行僧とは程遠く、ただの寒苦鳥としか言いようがない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「あー、もう無理！こんな修行、寒苦鳥の私には到底できないよ。」と彼は嘆いた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "昔から、困難を避け、楽ばかりしようとする者を寒苦鳥と呼んだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "怠惰な彼は、少しの苦労もせず、まるで寒苦鳥のようだった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
